- title_and_header = 'Incorrect vehicle details'
- page_title(title_and_header)

= render 'common/js_back_link'

%main.govuk-main-wrapper#main-content{role: 'main'}
  .govuk-grid-row
    .govuk-grid-column-two-thirds
      %h1.govuk-heading-l= title_and_header
      %p
        If your vehicle details are incorrect, you can
        = succeed '.' do
          = link_to_dvla_contact_form('contact us')
      %p
        You still need to pay a charge if you have driven, or are planning to drive, in the zone.
      %p
        If your vehicle does meet emission standards, you can claim a
        = link_to('refund',
                  'https://www.gov.uk/guidance/driving-in-a-clean-air-zone',
                  id: 'refund-link')
        from the Local Authority after your registration details have been updated.

      = link_to('Continue',
                undetermined_vehicle? ? not_determined_vehicles_path : local_authority_charges_path,
                class: 'govuk-button',
                'data-module': 'govuk-button')
      %p
        = link_to('Check another vehicle', enter_details_vehicles_path)
